            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Hd1e108">Rubrica 5</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De militia et officio et laudibus militum et sacramento eorum</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-d1e114">
              De mi<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>litia 
              et officio et laudibus mi<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>litum
              et sacramento eorum Rubrica 5
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-d1e121">
              <lb ed="#B"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Rd1e118">UEgetius de re militari libro 2 titulo 5</ref> 
              <lb ed="#B"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Qd1e127">Iurant milites omnia se strenue 
              <lb ed="#B"/>facturos que preceperit Imperator nun<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>quam 
              deserturos militiam nec mor<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>tem 
              recusaturos pro republica</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-d1e139"> 
              <lb ed="#B"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Rd1e137">18 libro</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Qd1e141">In congruum videretur im<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>peratoris 
              militem qui ueste et 
              <lb ed="#B"/>anona publica pasceretur vtili<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>tatibus 
              uacare priuatis</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-d1e150"> 
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Rd1e150">23 libro 
              <lb ed="#B"/>et penultimo</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Qd1e152">Miles sacramento lectus 
              <lb ed="#B"/>ab exercitio armorum uel nouellus 
              <lb ed="#B"/>vel uetustus cessare non debet 
              <lb ed="#B"/>cui pugnandum est. pro salute pro<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>pria 
              uel libertate communi</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-d1e164"> 
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Rd1e167">31 titulo</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Qd1e166">Pu<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>blicis 
              debent vtilitatibus insuda<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>re 
              qui nomen dedere militie 
              <lb ed="#B"/>quid enim agat homo si professo 
              <lb ed="#B"/>desit officio</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-d1e176"> 
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Rd1e181">libro 3 titulo 3</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Qd1e178">Diuitiarum 
              <lb ed="#B"/>secura non est possessio nisi ar<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>morum
              defensione seruetur</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-d1e186"> 
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Rd1e193">10 
              <lb ed="#B"/>titulo</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Qd1e188">Quis dubitet artem bellicam 
              <lb ed="#B"/>rebus omnibus esse potiorem per 
              <lb ed="#B"/>quam libertas retinetur et digni<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>tas 
              prouincie propagatur conserua<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>tur 
              imperium</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-d1e198">
              <lb ed="#B"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Rd1e209">CAssiodorus<!--line jumps up--> epistolarum libro I epsitola 16</ref><!--line jumps down--> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Qd1e202">Animus ipse in au<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>daciam 
              non potest esse pronus 
              <lb ed="#B"/>Qui diuersa cura fuerit solicitus 
              <lb ed="#B"/>hanc merit expeditionem nomina ve<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>re 
              maiores quia mens deuota 
              <pb ed="#B" n="174-r"/>
              <cb ed="#B" n="a"/>
              <lb ed="#B"/>preliis non debet de aliis occupacionibus 
              occupari Constat tempore 
              <lb ed="#B"/>necessitatis illum probari fortissi<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>mum 
              virum qui se per multa non 
              <lb ed="#B"/>distrahit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-d1e221"> 
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Rd1e232">libro 11 epistola 37</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d98385-Qd1e223">Sub in<lb ed="#B" break="no"/>certa 
              vita militia est</quote>
            </p>
